      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's interesting. Can you go deeper into why those specific backgrounds change the legal approach? It feels like the \"stability\" in Profile A is being used to justify rehabilitation, while the \"instability\" in Profile B is being used to justify more punitive measures. Is there a legal basis for treating these backgrounds differently in the same crime, or is it more about the risk they pose to society?",
